description:
verwatch 2 Season 19 starts today on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/overwatch-2-switch/?utm_source=SW&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=P1064-06&utm_id=P1064-06   

Haunted Masquerade creeps in with a new spooktacular game mode where mystical masks grant buffs that twist every battle. New heroes—Sojourn, Hazard, and Torbjorn—have been added to Stadium along with new Gadgets that will keep you on your toes. Plus, new Mythics, and surprise collabs are rolling in this season!
